location.fullValue: Isola Bella Estates - Villages Of Windsor 1

data.description:
Location! Location! Location! Gorgeous 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom Tiepolo model nestled by the serene embrace of a lakeside view, complete with a refreshing pool and inviting spa. It provides a long, beautiful view of the lake, with plenty of Large Mouth Bass and Peacock Bass for the avid fisherman & is far enough away from the nearest roads so that you can enjoy that this peaceful, quiet lake location provides you with. You can also enjoy the views from the recently completely renovated swimming pool. This residence is poised for personalization, awaiting the unique touch that will transform it into your dream home.... The first floor boasts seamless ceramic tile flooring, with lofty 10-foot ceilings enhancing the spacious feel, a formal living room, elegant dining area, expansive family room & large chef style kitchen. A versatile bedroom and a full bathroom on the first floor provide flexibility for guests, an office, or a cozy den, with the bathroom conveniently serving as a cabana bath. Ascend to the second floor, where plush carpeting adorns the bedrooms. Discover a walk-in pantry, central island, and a laundry room furnished with a washer and dryer. The master bedroom on the second floor exudes luxury, featuring a coffered ceiling, two spacious walk-in closets, and a master bath with dual sinks, vanities, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. Three additional bedrooms and a well-appointed hall bathroom complete the upper level.

A 3-car garage with extra storage space adds practicality to this already remarkable abode. Located just minutes away from upscale shopping, dining, and more, this home is situated in a meticulously maintained community that offers resort-style amenities for its residents. Your oasis awaits in this splendid haven of comfort and style. The schools are all A Rated including a brand new high school that just opened in September. The 1.2 million square foot Wellington Green Mall less than 10 minutes away is chock full of a wonderful selection of stores, restaurants and a new state of the art theater.

The only reason that this home is for sale is because the children grew up and married.
